  <RulesElement name="Shielding" type="Weapon Property" internal-id="ID_FMP_WEAPON_PROPERTY_20" source="Core" revision-date="2/18/2010 8:34:49 AM">
Whenever you hit at least one target with an attack power using a shielding implement, you gain a +1 shield bonus to AC and Reflex until the start of your next turn.
   </RulesElement>
  <RulesElement name="Forceful" type="Weapon Property" internal-id="ID_FMP_WEAPON_PROPERTY_19" source="Core" revision-date="2/18/2010 8:34:29 AM">
Whenever you pull, push, or slide a target with an attack power using a forceful implement, the distance of the forced movement increases by 1 square.
   </RulesElement>
