  <RulesElement name="Empowered Crit" type="Weapon Property" internal-id="ID_FMP_WEAPON_PROPERTY_17" source="Core" revision-date="2/18/2010 8:33:38 AM">
When you score a critical hit with an empowered crit implement, the attack deals 1d10 extra damage. The extra damage increases to 2d10 at 11th level and 3d10 at 21st level.
   </RulesElement>
  <RulesElement name="Distant" type="Weapon Property" internal-id="ID_FMP_WEAPON_PROPERTY_16" source="Core" revision-date="2/18/2010 8:33:16 AM">
The range of your area and ranged attack powers increases by 2 when they're used through a distant implement.
   </RulesElement>
  <RulesElement name="Deadly" type="Weapon Property" internal-id="ID_FMP_WEAPON_PROPERTY_15" source="Core" revision-date="2/18/2010 8:32:54 AM">
You gain a +1 bonus to damage rolls made with a deadly implement. The bonus increases to +2 at 11th level and +3 at 21st level.
   </RulesElement>
  <RulesElement name="Accurate" type="Weapon Property" internal-id="ID_FMP_WEAPON_PROPERTY_14" source="Core" revision-date="2/18/2010 8:32:30 AM">
